<LocalizedProperties><Language>en</Language><Title>Security Update for Windows XP (329834)</Title><Description>This update resolves the "Unchecked Buffer in PPTP Implementation Could Enable Denial of Service" security vulnerability in Windows XP and Windows XP Service Pack 1 (SP1). Download now to help prevent an attacker from disrupting service on a server that offers private networking and uses the PPTP protocol.</Description><UninstallNotes>Uninstall is available Add/Remove Programs.</UninstallNotes><MoreInfoUrl>http://www.download.windowsupdate.com/msdownload/update/v3/static/RTF/en/5780.htm</MoreInfoUrl><SupportUrl>http://support.microsoft.com</SupportUrl></LocalizedProperties>